org.hyperic.hq.hqapi1
Class AgentApi

java.lang.Object
  org.hyperic.hq.hqapi1.AgentApi

public class AgentApi
extends java.lang.Object

The Hyperic HQ Agent API.

This class provides access to the agents within the HQ system. Each of the methods in this class return Response objects that wrap the result of the method with a ResponseStatus and a ServiceError that indicates the error if the response status is ResponseStatus.FAILURE.
